snippet: The boat, packed with up to 250 African migrants trying to reach Europe, sank east of Tripoli, and only 26 people have been rescued so far, the Libyan Navy said.
abstract: Boat carrying as many as 250 African migrants trying to reach Europe sinks off coast of Libya; most passengers are feared dead.
lead_paragraph: The boat, packed with up to 250 African migrants trying to reach Europe, sank east of Tripoli, and only 26 people have been rescued so far, the Libyan Navy said.
